itemDescription: Ugandan/British Entrepreneur, Innovator and Thought Leader

wikipedia_page.main: Nataliey Bitature (born 1989), is a Ugandan entrepreneur and executive, currently serving as Chief of Staff at The Simba Group. Bitature was named in the Forbes 30 Under 30 in 2015 and is the daughter of Patrick Bitature, one of the richest people in Uganda.

response: *Nataliey Bitature, 2016 World Economic Forum's Top 5 African Innovators & 2014 Forbes 30 Under 30
Bitature is married to Carol Bitature and has four children. Nataliey Bitature is one of his children.
